'''Bill Black''' was the publisher, editor, Chairman of the Board, and founder of AC Comics (original Americomics). He was an inker for several issues of [[Dark Horse Comics]], including ''[[Tales of the Jedi: The Golden Age of the Sith (TPB)]]'', [[Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi — The Fall of the Sith Empire|''Tales of the Jedi: The Fall of the Sith Empire'']], ''[[Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi &mdash; The Sith War]]'', and ''[[Jedi Academy: Leviathan]]''.

